&lt;p&gt;We have an opportunities for Band 5 registered Nurses to join our dynamic team on Sirhowy Ward at Ysbyty Aneurin Bevan.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sirhowy Ward consists of 32 rehabilitation/subacute beds ywo of which can be allocated to dirct Community Admissions for the Community resource team in Blaenau Gwent.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are looking for an new opportunity to develop or consolidate you skills please contact us and we will be happy to discuss the posts with you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 19th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Diane Thomas, Ward Manager&lt;br /&gt;Diane.Thomas6@wales.nhs.uk&lt;br /&gt;01495 363330&lt;/p&gt;
